'''Saurians''' were a [[Reptile/Legends|reptilian]] [[Species/Legends|race]] with [[Snake/Legends|snake]]-like heads. They spoke with a lisp and generally wore swamp-patterned fatigues. [[Sithless Leethe]] and [[Slopper]] were both members of this species.

